Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:03:02.46,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1600,1200)}{\pos(320,320)}最强的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.82,0:24:10.86,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1300,0)}{\pos(320,340)}两个魔术师<前篇>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:10.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如想辞退Master一职
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:12.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比把圣杯拿到手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:14.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现自己的愿望更好的办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:21.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想消除这肉眼所看不见的烧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:24.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需接受那圣痕便行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:25.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:28.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作为被选中的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:31.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有无为此圣杯战争而战斗的意向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:33.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:00.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好  大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:02.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样见面已经是第二次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:05.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  这家伙和我们不是一个层次的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:08.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:12.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伊利雅  伊利雅斯菲尔·冯·阿因兹贝伦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:12.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimhei}{\pos(320,25)}{\fs16}Illyasviel·Von·Einzbern
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:14.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说该明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:16.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿因兹贝伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:19.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打招呼到此为止就可以了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:21.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你们都会死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:24.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  杀掉你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:26.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉他们  Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:26.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimhei}{\pos(320,28)}{\fs18}Berserker{\fn方正隶变简体}：狂战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎  退后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:08.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:24.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的巨剑在他手中如同玩具一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:27.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉他们  干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:56.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:03:59.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker  就在那里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气了结她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:22.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:26.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:29.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:32.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远坂…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:37.63,Niaoyu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Vier Stil　Erschiesung」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:37.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\pos(340,325)}四式射杀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙的身体到底是什么构成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:51.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:52.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧  Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:10.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:18.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:21.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没可能打赢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:00.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是希腊最强的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希腊最强的英雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:04.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:07.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错哦  在这里的就是名为赫拉克勒斯的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:07.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,28)}{\fs18}赫拉克勒斯：希腊最伟大的英雄,曾立下十二件功勋（十二试炼）,死后成神。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:10.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫拉克勒斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:15.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  是跟你们这种程度所役使的英雄有天壤之别
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:17.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最强的怪物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:25.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从头部开始砍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:23.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那家伙还会再生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:36.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:43.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:11.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:13.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:17.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:30.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  这样真有够无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:31.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:39.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:42.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再见面的时候会杀掉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:01.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  已经没办法再救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:22.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候  我曾经很憧憬正义的伙伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为什么啊  曾经很憧憬？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经放弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄是有保质期的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:35.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长大成人以后就很难这样自称了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:41.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情  再早一些察觉到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:47.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:49.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话也没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  真的是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:54.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没办法  所以由我来代替你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:00.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然老爸已经是成人没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:02.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的话一定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:11.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧  我一定会好好把老爸的梦想实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:14.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:45.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:09:59.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:05.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:11.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擅自泡了茶  卫宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:19.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为  为什么你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:24.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来连像样点的茶叶都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:28.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡茶的袋子至少也准备个三角形的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:31.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远坂  你为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:32.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:36.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前  应该先谢谢我把你搬到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬到这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:48.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我被那个怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:59.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  为什么我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:12.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  为什么我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:15.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后你的伤自动愈合了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:16.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己愈合是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:20.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我看来Saber好像也有自我治疗的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可能是那能力流到你身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:32.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由Sevent给Master提供魔力什么的本来是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你也是个出人意料的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:37.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:41.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去救Servant的Master真是闻所未闻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:45.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死了的话Saber也就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:50.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫宫同学  接下来你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:58.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想重蹈十年前的覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:03.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对圣杯那种东西没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:05.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:09.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  说那种话会被Saber杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:11.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被Saber…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:15.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为Servant会无条件地服从人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:19.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把圣杯拿到手就能实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:23.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对于身为守护者的Servant也不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:26.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们之所以回应Master的召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:28.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了能拿到圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:31.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现自己各种各样的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:34.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了圣杯Saber会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是Saber是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:43.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚还流了那么多的血
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:46.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对Servant而言是没有生死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:49.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使丧命也只是回到原本的地方而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此而互相残杀什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:54.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就这样放着别的Master不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:56.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无辜的人就会死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:01.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Servant的燃料是魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积蓄的魔力越是多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:07.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就越能自由使用生前的特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:09.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们是灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉灵魂的话就能获得营养
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:19.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说也有为了补充魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:23.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而指使Servant袭击人类并吃掉其灵魂的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Servant会吃人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:35.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…不对  Saber是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:40.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:44.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论其他的Master做什么你都袖手旁观吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话只有阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是败给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说自己不会去打倒其他Master
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:52.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是当他做坏事的时候却又要去打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:58.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你自己是矛盾的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这样很自私
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:05.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想不到其他的行动方针
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:12.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个问题  可以说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:18.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的Master肯定会来杀我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:23.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子的Servant层次和我们不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去可以说是坐以待毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连自己都无法保护吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:34.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个Servant是叫赫拉克勒斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:37.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是被藐视得可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄的真名被知道了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:41.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等于是把自己的弱点暴露给敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:44.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  Saber的真名是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:47.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是不要知道的比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:50.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对别人  口风好像不是很紧的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人  是指远坂你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:56.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不记得和你是自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:00.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不用送我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:03.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我搬回家的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:08.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记说了  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:21.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后别把我当成人类看待会比较轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:32.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣杯战争
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:36.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦参加就必须打倒所有的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:42.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打倒对手  甚至去加害毫无关系的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:45.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做点什么的话  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆幸吧  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:52.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于可以如愿以偿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:10.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  我想拯救别人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:13.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让任何人死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:15.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎  退后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:20.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber一心想要保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都成那样子了还…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:27.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  Saber呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  樱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:40.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  为什么这个时候会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:43.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是早睡早起的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在散步啊  散步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:00.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血的…味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:07.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:10.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤村老师  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:13.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人清爽的早晨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:16.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种日子真想去吃点麦芽饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得有做好海味小菜放在家里的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海味小菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:25.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还浓厚多汁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  从早上开始就情绪高涨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得帮我多留几碗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎已经找遍整个屋子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:43.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:48.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色不太好的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:46.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:48.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:52.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  士郎  关于昨晚的事我有话想和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:53.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:57.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master有着那样的行为会让我很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:01.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗是我的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:04.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎请做好自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:07.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为Master的你没有保护我的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:13.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救女孩子还需要理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:18.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再问一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:21.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你Saber可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  既然作为Servant和你订立契约之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:26.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是士郎的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:30.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为了赢得圣杯战争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:33.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:35.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:39.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是Saber  你跟着我胜算很小哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:42.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是说你没有战斗的意向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:44.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的意向是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:47.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  无论结果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:49.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是我决定的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:50.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是没有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:56.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有胜算的话  就由我来创造
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:19:59.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用有可能的所有方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:04.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道  为了得到力量而袭击人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:07.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是没可能会使用的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害手无寸铁的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有违骑士道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:28.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果是Master的命令就只有遵从
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:33.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候作为践踏我尊严的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:36.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是必须要使用一个刻印
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:39.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我绝不让那种事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:43.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:48.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不知不觉中侮辱了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:50.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  请抬起头来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:53.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是不知道士郎的意图
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就妄自猜测了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:04.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然全是些不明白的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:08.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也只能凭借在我们能力范围以内的行动去解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:13.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:18.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空腹是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:20.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃饭吧  士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:33.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:37.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  你早上习惯吃和食吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:41.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  只要是能吃的东西  什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:42.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奢侈是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:45.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人还真多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:47.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:52.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  虽然尽是些难以置信的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:55.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不也有能让人相信的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.30,0:22:00.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber不是冷酷的杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:03.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber是…
